item.dc:creator: @Pheega Pheega
item.description:
@Pheega wrote:

[quote=“jjones10, post:9, topic:281942”]Okay nice comment: That is seriously amazing for a first model. you need some more rep =]
Critisism: i know you are new, but 3.5 hours is a long time. The bottom of the handle looks strange… the handle needs to be round… and thats it! Very very good job[/quote]Yeah it took 3.5 hours because I was trying to do it without the mirror function, eventually I figured it out and finished it quickly. The handle can’t be round because irl if the handle was round the axe would spin around in your hands
Thanks for the criticism though.
